TaskFlow Elite
A professional productivity dashboard built with Vue 3, TypeScript, and Vuetify.
Setup

Clone the repository.
Navigate to the core directory and run npm install followed by npm run build.
Navigate to the ui directory and run npm install followed by npm run dev.
Open http://localhost:5173 in your browser.

Features

Task management with CRUD operations.
Analytics chart showing task completion rate.
Dark mode toggle.

Architecture

Core logic is in a separate TypeScript library (core).
UI is built with Vue 3, using Vite for development and build.
State management with Pinia.
Routing with Vue Router.
UI components with Vuetify.

Testing

Unit tests for core logic using Vitest.
